data.description: Walkout 2 story home that was expanded from the original floor plan so all rooms are oversized & spacious! Situated on a west facing lot in the Millard West High School area! There are 5 bedrooms, 4 bathrooms, 3 car garage, & 3,646 sq ft.  Excellent curb appeal w/ porch.  Gorgeous kitchen w/ gray cabinets, quartz countertops, pantry, & staggered plank LVP flooring.   Large primary suite w/ 2 closets. Convenient 2nd floor laundry room AND 2nd laundry location in basement.  Finished basement that is laid out great w/ rec room, 5th bedroom, & bathroom. You’ll love all of the windows & natural sunlight throughout the home.  Fully fenced backyard.  Extra parking pad on driveway.  Such a great home for the money!
